#. Tag: para
#: man-kpat.6.docbook:40
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kpatience; is a compendium of several well known patience card games, "
#| "ranging from the well known Klondike and Freecell, to lesser known games "
#| "such as Grandfather's Clock and Mod3. In all there are 13 variations for "
#| "you to while away time."
msgid ""
"&kpatience; is a compendium of several well known patience card games, "
"ranging from the well known Klondike and Freecell, to lesser known games "
"such as Grandfather's Clock and Mod3. In all there are 12 variations for you "
"to while away time."
msgstr ""
"&kpatience; - это подборка нескольких популярных пасьянсов, начиная от "
"Косынки и Свободной ячейки, и заканчивая Дедушкиными часами и Mod3, а всего "
"тринадцать вариантов чем-нибудь занять себя в свободное время."

